725535f-b.title: Queens: 63rd Street - Queens Boulevard
725535f-b.text:
63rd Street, east side, north of Queens Boulevard to
Hicks Drive, showing in the background of both views the
William Sackett house. See other views written at same location
but south from Woodside Avenue for more data.
March 1925.
View 21 April 1925.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection
